                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.14579/2606.14579v1/x2.png",
                "caption": "Figure 2:Overview of VISTA.VISTA constructs GRPO groups from target-preserving views of the same GUI grounding instance.\nModel rollouts define the group statistics, while an oracle-format center-point anchor is activated only for self-verified groups.",
